title: Avengers Disassembled
description:
This package includes the digital release of the hard to find Avengers Disassembled storyline. This is the conclusion of the vintage era of Avengers which let Brian Michael Bendis start the Avengers and most of the Marvel Universe over from scratch.

It paved the way for Civil War and every other universe defining storyline to follow.

Also in this torrent is the House of M series as well as The New Avengers #26.

Why would I do this?

Because this torrent is really called "That Time They Killed Hawkeye Dead. Twice."
